      "type": "RESPONSE",
      "payload": "# Caffeine Content in Coca-Cola\n\nA standard 12 oz (355 ml) can of **Coca-Cola contains approximately 34 mg of caffeine**.\n\n## Other Coca-Cola Products:\n- **Coca-Cola Diet/Zero**: ~46 mg per 12 oz\n- **Coca-Cola Cherry**: ~34 mg per 12 oz\n- **20 oz bottle**: ~57 mg\n- **2-liter bottle (per 12 oz serving)**: ~34 mg\n\n## Context:\n- This is roughly **one-third the caffeine** of a typical cup of brewed coffee (~95 mg per 8 oz)\n- Coca-Cola's caffeine comes from **kola nuts and synthetic caffeine**\n- Caffeine content can vary slightly by region and formulation\n\nFor the most current information, you can check the nutrition label on the specific product you're interested in.",
